sequenceDiagram
  participant U as user
  participant A as CLI Agent
  participant T as Tool Runtime
  participant S as Session Log
  participant L as Candidate Ledger
  participant G as Governance
  participant M as Governance Store

  U->>A: Fix failed tests
  A->>T: Read package.json
  T-->>S: observation: scripts.test
  A->>T: Run related tests
  T-->>S: observation: Failure log
  A->>T: Modify the code and verify
  T-->>S: observation: Test passed
  S->>L: Extract candidate memories
  L->>G: Source/Scope/TTL/Conflict Checking
  G-->>L: status update
  G->>M: Approvals are written to long-term memory
